      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Scratchings have decimated the race, leaving only three runners. SEAMS LOGICAL (3) resumes after a break of four months. Looking to emulate his debut win over 800m at Warwick to kick off last prep. Placed in a recent trial and is sure to go well. EMBOLDEN (6) made late ground and finished second last time over 800m at Warwick when resuming from a spell, beaten 1.2 lengths. In the right race and is one of the big hopes. BETTERINDANUDE (2) is lining up for a winning hat-trick after scoring on turf over 800m at this track two back then following up with a win on dirt over 1000m at Taroom more recently. In form and another bold showing is expected.",
